Scorched  Tanks,  but  in Workbench. The respect of the operating system is
always my watchword. This game is freeware.

	Author  is NOT responsible for any damage (or damages !) attributed
to  Workbench Army. You are warned that you play Workbench Army at your own
risk !!!

