				=======


Workbench Army 2.00 (BETA 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8)
------------------------------------------
	* english version (not czech)
	* random landscape
	* destruction of landscape
	* new sounds (1/2 of EXE file)
	* five weapons :
		1 Single Shot
		2 Big Shot
		3 Very Big Shot
		4 Mini Nuke
		5 Mega Nuke
	* tooltypes (you can change the default settings on startup)
        * biger window
	* fixed many bugs (like always)
	* a bit faster
	* and more



Workbench Army 1.xx 
-------------------
